      "text": "「絶対に負けない時」……か\n確かに、見定めるのは難しいよな",
      "startTime": 223.3333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui023.m4a",
      "text": "はい。私達は今も、そしてこれからも\n自分達を高め続けていくつもりです",
      "startTime": 231.3666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
